  "body": "### Description of the Issue\r\n\r\nCannot sign messages on https://beta.mycrypto.com/sign-and-verify-message/sign with Ledger Nano S\r\n\r\n### Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Go to https://beta.mycrypto.com/sign-and-verify-message/sign\r\n2. Open the Ethereum app on my Ledger Nano S\r\n3. Click \"Connect to Ledger Wallet\"\r\n4. Select my address, click \"Unlock\"\r\n5. Enter a message\r\n6. Click sign message\r\n7. Check my Ledger -- I see a message that says \"Sign the message\" and then the message hash\r\n8. Click the right button (check mark) on my Ledger\r\n9. Nothing happens ... \r\n\r\nI tested it on the production site and signing works fine with the same Ledger.\r\n\r\n### Description of Your Machine\r\n\r\nWindows 10 / Chrome\r\n\r\n### Console Logs / Screenshots\r\n\r\nNothing special -- no errors in the console.\r\n",
